								&raquo; Profil und Artikel
							</a></div></li><li class="list__item"><a class="list__header-link" href="/autor/nicole-zillien/?tx_ngfhpublications_people%5Baction%5D=show&amp;cHash=166e1e9772ca73a9995c7aa1d420df3d"><h3 class="list__header">
