							</a></div></li><li class="list__item"><a class="list__header-link" href="/autor/harro-zimmermann/?tx_ngfhpublications_people%5Baction%5D=show&amp;cHash=bbcf6d1ab8313ba6c5c94905d736f10c"><h3 class="list__header">
