							</a></div></li><li class="list__item"><a class="list__header-link" href="/autor/klaus-f-zimmermann/?tx_ngfhpublications_people%5Baction%5D=show&amp;cHash=baafc2ed081ab6080fc96f229bdbbf93"><h3 class="list__header">
